# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:15
translate portuguese jamietv3_917dd9af:

    # "I follow Jamie into the living room and sit down on the couch next to her."
    "Sigo a Jamie até à sala e sento-me no sofá ao lado dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:18
translate portuguese jamietv3_8105064d:

    # "She smiles at me and we both turn towards the TV and watch the show."
    "Ela sorri para mim e ambos nos viramos para a televisão e vemos o programa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:21
translate portuguese jamietv3_916367bf:

    # "After the first commercial break, Jamie looks over at me."
    "Após o primeiro intervalo publicitário, a Jamie olha para mim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:22
translate portuguese jamietv3_cdf30048:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. Do you want to put your arm around me?"
    gnd "Ei, [pcname]. Queres passar o braço à minha volta?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamietv3_804b08d6:

    # "I slip my arm behind her neck and around her shoulder, my hand resting on her arm."
    "Deslizo o meu braço por trás do pescoço dela e à volta do ombro, com a mão pousada no braço dela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamietv3_1d9d9b4f:

    # "She leans into me, putting her head on my shoulder."
    "Ela inclina-se para mim, pousando a cabeça no meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamietv3_4ea3c230:

    # gnd "I like this. You feel so nice."
    gnd "Gosto disto. És tão agradável."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:32
translate portuguese jamietv3_7ebbf022:

    # pc "You feel pretty nice yourself."
    pc "Tu também és bastante agradável."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:33
translate portuguese jamietv3_8813a725:

    # "We watch the rest of the show like that, me holding her with her body pressed against mine."
    "Assistimos ao resto do programa assim, eu a abraçá-la com o corpo dela pressionado contra o meu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:35
translate portuguese jamietv3_37e4900f:

    # "Then, the show ends and she looks up at me."
    "Então, o programa acaba e ela olha para mim."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:36
translate portuguese jamietv3_1d242ffe:

    # "She has that look in her eyes again. I'm sure that she wants me to kiss her."
    "Ela tem aquele olhar nos olhos outra vez. Tenho a certeza de que ela quer que eu a beije."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:42
translate portuguese jamietv3_a52d94e4:

    # "I'm not really all that interested in Jamie as more than a friend."
    "Na verdade, não estou assim tão interessado na Jamie como mais do que uma amiga."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:43
translate portuguese jamietv3_d89f8402:

    # pc "I should probably go home."
    pc "Provavelmente devia ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:47
translate portuguese jamietv3_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:48
translate portuguese jamietv3_34e40ec9:

    # gnd "Oh, okay."
    gnd "Oh, está bem."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamietv3_113f6693:

    # gnd "I guess I'll see you later then."
    gnd "Acho que nos vemos mais tarde, então."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:50
translate portuguese jamietv3_6e2174f7:

    # pc "Bye, Jamie."
    pc "Adeus, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:52
translate portuguese jamietv3_02f80202:

    # "I let myself out and walk back over to my house."
    "Saio e caminho de volta para minha casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:53
translate portuguese jamietv3_467f2c00:

    # "I can tell she is disappointed, but I just don't feel anything for her right now."
    "Dá para perceber que ela está desapontada, mas simplesmente não sinto nada por ela neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:54
translate portuguese jamietv3_0101b10c:

    # "Hopefully we can still be friends."
    "Espero que ainda possamos ser amigos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:58
translate portuguese jamietv3_6814bb66:

    # "I take the opportunity and lean in to kiss her."
    "Aproveito a oportunidade e inclino-me para a beijar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamietv3_778ff7ef:

    # "Her lips are so soft and warm. She presses her mouth against mine eagerly."
    "Os lábios dela são tão macios e quentes. Ela pressiona a boca contra a minha com entusiasmo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:64
translate portuguese jamietv3_eb54665e:

    # "Then, finally we part and gaze into each other's eyes."
    "Depois, finalmente separamo-nos e olhamos nos olhos um do outro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:66
translate portuguese jamietv3_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_012.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_012.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:67
translate portuguese jamietv3_0fadec5c:

    # gnd "You have no idea how long I've wanted that."
    gnd "Não fazes ideia de há quanto tempo eu queria isto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamietv3_9accb448:

    # pc "Same."
    pc "Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:69
translate portuguese jamietv3_d11f6ea7:

    # "I hear her dad's car pull up into the driveway then, and know that our night is over."
    "Ouço o carro do pai dela a entrar na entrada e sei que a nossa noite acabou."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:70
translate portuguese jamietv3_20bbfb99:

    # pc "Maybe next time we start with the kissing and don't worry so much about the show?"
    pc "Talvez da próxima vez comecemos pelos beijos e não nos preocupemos tanto com o espetáculo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:71
translate portuguese jamietv3_ef71a0ee:

    # gnd "But I like the show."
    gnd "Mas eu gosto do espetáculo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:72
translate portuguese jamietv3_4e3c3496:

    # pc "I like the kissing."
    pc "Eu gosto dos beijos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamietv3_130159a8:

    # gnd "I like the kissing too. We'll see."
    gnd "Eu também gosto dos beijos. Veremos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:74
translate portuguese jamietv3_faa1bb12:

    # "Her dad walks in and doesn't even look at us as he walks into the kitchen."
    "O pai dela entra e nem sequer olha para nós enquanto se dirige para a cozinha."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:75
translate portuguese jamietv3_d862e92d:

    # gnd "You better go. He seems grumpy."
    gnd "É melhor ires. Ele parece mal-humorado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:76
translate portuguese jamietv3_b4408fea:

    # pc "Alright. We'll do this again sometime though?"
    pc "Está bem. Mas vamos repetir isto um dia destes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:77
translate portuguese jamietv3_0d1ee4ed:

    # gnd "Definitely."
    gnd "Com certeza."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:81
translate portuguese jamietv3_e768df10:

    # "She walks with me out to her front porch."
    "Ela acompanha-me até à varanda da frente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:82
translate portuguese jamietv3_72addde0:

    # gnd "I had a great time tonight."
    gnd "Diverti-me imenso esta noite."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:83
translate portuguese jamietv3_03eaad50:

    # pc "Me too."
    pc "Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:84
translate portuguese jamietv3_0a7ec385:

    # gnd "One more before you leave?"
    gnd "Mais um antes de ires embora?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:85
translate portuguese jamietv3_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:87
translate portuguese jamietv3_de9ce80b:

    # "I pull her close and we kiss one more time."
    "Puxo-a para perto de mim e beijamo-nos mais uma vez."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:88
translate portuguese jamietv3_f8d91f0b:

    # "I want more, but what could I do right now?"
    "Quero mais, mas o que posso fazer agora?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:89
translate portuguese jamietv3_56e3f7c6:

    # "Eventually, we pull away from each other."
    "Por fim, afastamo-nos um do outro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:91
translate portuguese jamietv3_650dddc0:

    # gnd "Bye, [pcname]. See you again soon."
    gnd "Adeus, [pcname]. Até breve."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamietv3_6e2174f7_1:

    # pc "Bye, Jamie."
    pc "Adeus, Jamie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamietv3_2d3eec63:

    # "She goes back inside and shuts the door, likely off to make dinner for her father, to soothe his seemingly constant anger."
    "Ela volta para dentro e fecha a porta, provavelmente para preparar o jantar para o pai, para acalmar a sua raiva aparentemente constante."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:94
translate portuguese jamietv3_d669211e:

    # "I walk back to my house, wishing that I could spend more time with her."
    "Volto para casa, desejando poder passar mais tempo com ela."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:102
translate portuguese jamietv3b_78d17b7d:

    # pc "I don't mean to hurt your feelings or anything, but I'm not really interested in you as more than a friend."
    pc "Não quero magoar-te nem nada, mas não estou realmente interessado em ti como mais do que uma amiga."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:106
translate portuguese jamietv3b_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:107
translate portuguese jamietv3b_74617460:

    # gnd "Oh. Okay then. Friends."
    gnd "Oh. Está bem, então. Amigos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:108
translate portuguese jamietv3b_5bc18a87:

    # "I can tell that she is disappointed, but I'm just not feeling anything for her right now."
    "Dá para perceber que ela está desapontada, mas simplesmente não sinto nada por ela neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:111
translate portuguese jamietv3b_1e43d4a9:

    # "We watch the rest of the show in silence."
    "Assistimos ao resto do programa em silêncio."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:112
translate portuguese jamietv3b_27eeafbd:

    # "It's awkward."
    "É estranho."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:116
translate portuguese jamietv3b_79945408:

    # "Then, when it's over, she quickly ushers me outside and waves goodbye."
    "Depois, quando acaba, ela rapidamente me acompanha até à porta e acena em despedida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:117
translate portuguese jamietv3b_34730410:

    # gnd "Bye friend. See you later."
    gnd "Adeus, amigo. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:118
translate portuguese jamietv3b_a3355754:

    # "Before I can answer, she goes back inside and closes the door."
    "Antes que eu consiga responder, ela volta para dentro e fecha a porta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv3.rpy:119
translate portuguese jamietv3b_14b47581:

    # "I walk back home, wondering if it would even be possible for us to remain friends. It seems unlikely."
    "Volto para casa a pé, a pensar se será mesmo possível continuarmos amigos. Parece improvável."

